<p data-start="17" data-end="46">To make that image your logo:</p>
<h3 data-section-id="zej43w" data-start="48" data-end="73">Step 1: Save the logo</h3>
<ol data-start="74" data-end="149">
<li data-section-id="uonsg2" data-start="74" data-end="104">
<p data-start="77" data-end="104">Right-click the logo image.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1au82ul" data-start="105" data-end="134">
<p data-start="108" data-end="134">Click <strong data-start="114" data-end="134">Save image as...</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="do19sc" data-start="135" data-end="149">
<p data-start="138" data-end="149">Save it as:</p>
</li>
</ol>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="151" data-end="171"><div class="relative w-full mt-4 mb-1"><div class=""><div class="contents"><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button type="button" class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-9c5054d5.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="relative"><div class="pe-11 pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼd ͼr"><div class="cm-scroller"><pre class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly m-0"><code><span>logo.png</span></code></pre></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<h3 data-section-id="1etfjbw" data-start="173" data-end="204">Step 2: Upload it to GitHub</h3>
<ol data-start="205" data-end="343">
<li data-section-id="1xdk0c3" data-start="205" data-end="250">
<p data-start="208" data-end="250">Go to your <strong data-start="219" data-end="238">rr-pet-adoption</strong> repository.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="i1iq6y" data-start="251" data-end="292">
<p data-start="254" data-end="292">Click <strong data-start="260" data-end="272">Add file</strong> → <strong data-start="275" data-end="291">Upload files</strong>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1ms6byh" data-start="293" data-end="314">
<p data-start="296" data-end="314">Upload <code data-start="303" data-end="313">logo.png</code>.</p>
</li>
<li data-section-id="1lzw4hn" data-start="315" data-end="343">
<p data-start="318" data-end="343">Click <strong data-start="324" data-end="342">Commit changes</strong>.</p>
</li>
</ol>
<h3 data-section-id="18nwlm8" data-start="345" data-end="379">Step 3: Add it to your website</h3>
